com.ibm.jaggr.service.modulebuilder

Interface IModuleBuilderExtensionPoint


  • public interface IModuleBuilderExtensionPoint
    This interface defines constants for the modulebuilder extension point

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static String EXTENSION_ATTRIBUTE
      Name of modulebuilder extension point extension attribute.
      static String ID
      Name extension point id.
      static Class<?> INTERFACE
      A reference to the IModuleBuilder interface which is the interface that plugin extensions of the modulebuilder extension point must implement.
      static String NAME
      The extension point name.
      static String NAMESPACE
      The extension point namespace.
      static String[] REQUIRED_ATTRIBUTES
      List of required extension attributes for the modulebuilder extension point.

    • Field Detail

      • NAME

        static final String NAME
        The extension point name. This value is combined with the namespace for the extension point to form the extension point id.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • NAMESPACE

        static final String NAMESPACE
        The extension point namespace. This value is combined with the extension point name to form the extension point id.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ID

        static final String ID
        Name extension point id. This is the combination of the extension point namespace plus the extension point name.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • EXTENSION_ATTRIBUTE

        static final String EXTENSION_ATTRIBUTE
        Name of modulebuilder extension point extension attribute. Specifies the file extension (.js, .html, etc.), that this builder supports, or * if this builder can support all extensions.

        This is a required attribute.

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • REQUIRED_ATTRIBUTES

        static final String[] REQUIRED_ATTRIBUTES
        List of required extension attributes for the modulebuilder extension point.

      • INTERFACE

        static final Class<?> INTERFACE
        A reference to the IModuleBuilder interface which is the interface that plugin extensions of the modulebuilder extension point must implement.
